title: Boyce DiPrima 10th Ed.
description:
This is the 10th edition of the Boyce/DiPrima "Elementary Differential Equations" textbook. It does NOT include Chapters 10 & 11 on Boundary Value Problems. (May upload if I find those too)


The only difference between this book and previous editions is random problems moved around, new problems added, and a couple sections switched spots back in the 7th edition. THE MATH HAS BEEN THE SAME FOR DECADES. 

So fuck these guys, enjoy your book. :)
